data.description: Do not miss this beautiful 3 bed 2 bath home that has a country setting, but is only minutes from the city.  Great covered front and back porches, with a fenced in backyard, on almost a half acre and at the end of a dead end street.  Walk inside to a great living/dining room with a wood burning fireplace.  Large family room with a built in cabinet and shelving, and a bay window.  Large kitchen full of nice Haas cabinets, and plenty of counter space.  Pergo flooring throughout. Schedule your showing today!
